IDFSG Simulator Events are returning! <:idfsgs_gpoint:632261872174891012>
Hey everyone! You may be wondering about the game called IDFSG Simulator, which has a main event before - but you might be confused and thinking if the new event might start and ask; "When is it going to start?", "Has the main event been discontinued forever?" or "How long will it take for the main event to return?". Well, we are really proud to announce that I Don't Feel So Good Simulator events will now be returning in the future.

Yes, you heard that right! The title also says it in the announcement, and for those who didn't know or haven't heard about IDFSG Simulator events before, that's okay! I'll explain the history for all of the newest members who joined the server.

Back in the days in the year of 2019, IDFSG Simulator used to have the first event called Rocket Launch (known as the Rocket Event), where you get launched by a rocket and see the whole space by the planets. It was a pretty fun event, indeed. However, many revolutions of the timeline in the event were a lot getting interesting, and yet, there was another event called Multiverse. Multiverse used to travel along the past events; to the mysterious place we began, through the Light and Dark orbs, and other things you might know about it. there were 4 realms, including 1 realm that is our home to the normal world. However, that is for another time to begin a new journey to discover the history of our newest event to play..

When is the main event going to start?
We will be able to start the newest event here at Saturday or Sunday, and hopefully we'll be able to do some fun here. It might take some while to start, so stay tuned as we'll announce everyone to join in!

We hope to see you around in another time. Thanks for reading, and prepare for the newest adventure coming through! üìú
